---
import overviewImage from "../assets/images/bapp_overview.png";
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section class="px-[16px] md:px-[64px] lg:px-[80px] py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="container grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- Text -->
    <div>
      <span
        class="text-sm tracking-widest font-semibold text-[#018FF5] uppercase"
      >
        About BAPP
      </span>

      <h2
        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] leading-tights mt-4"
      >
        Reliable Fuel Distribution for Industry and Maritime Operations
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        PT Bumi Asri Prima Pratama (BAPP) has been delivering High Speed Diesel
        (HSD) and Marine Fuel Oil solutions to industrial, mining, offshore, and
        maritime sectors across Indonesia for over two decades.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 mb-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        With nationwide distribution coverage, bunker services, and strategic
        storage facilities, BAPP ensures stable supply performance, regulatory
        compliance, and operational continuity for high-demand industries.
      </p>
      <Button text="About Us" href="/about-us" />
    </div>

    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="relative">
      <img
        src={overviewImage.src}
        alt="Fuel storage and marine distribution facility"
        class="rounded-xl shadow-lg"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
